{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**Staleness detection** (`internal/adapters/docker/build.go`):","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922766042Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- `EnsureImage()` reads `.cloche/Dockerfile`, computes SHA-256 hash, and compares against a `cloche.dockerfile.hash` label stored on the image","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922769258Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- If the hash differs (Dockerfile changed) or the image doesn't exist, it rebuilds","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922779247Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Additionally checks if the base image (from `FROM` directive) has changed locally by comparing `cloche.baseimage.digest` label to current image ID","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922785438Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Labels are embedded during `docker build` for future comparisons","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.92279155Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922797471Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**Integration in daemon** (`internal/adapters/grpc/server.go:152-162`):","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922800246Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- `launchAndTrack()` calls `EnsureImage()` before starting the container","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922810335Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- If the rebuild fails, the run is marked as failed with a descriptive error message","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922817459Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922825614Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**Test coverage**:","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.92282884Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Unit tests for hash computation, Dockerfile parsing, no-Dockerfile case, base image staleness","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922832397Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"- Integration tests (Docker-dependent, skipped in this environment) for build-when-missing, skip-when-up-to-date, rebuild-on-change, base-digest storage","timestamp":"2026-03-08T01:37:28.922839641Z"}
